title: Chapel Hill dominates district meets
text: Contributed photo Junior high boys XC The Chapel Hill Junior High Red Devils won the district championship. Top row from left: Daniel Forest, Ociel Martinez, Derek Jones, Jorge Alvarez, Adrian Santiesteban, Samuel Netro, Kevin Reyes and Carter Nicholson. Bottom row from left: Taylor Agnew,Julian Ramirez, Jesus Alvarez, Grant Sparks. Contributed photo Varsity boys XC The Chapel Hill Red Devils won the district championship. Pictured, from left, are coach Brian Grissom, Zac Shipp, Bryant Roberts, Cole Posey, Josh Simmons, Will Phillips, Layton Faulkner, Will Rogers and coach Jody Simmons. Contributed photo Varsity girls XC The Lady Red Devils won the district championship. Pictured, from left, are coach Brian Grissom, Kaylyn Tompkins, Tara Lockaby, Christine Calvert, Jessica Stanley, Ashley Marquez, Marissa Ojendis and coach Jody Simmons. Contributed photo Junior high girls XC The Chapel Hill Junior High Lady Red Devils finished second overall in the District 16-3A cross country meet this past Saturday. Pictured, from left, are Nadia Hooks, Kirsten Nugent, Isabella O’dell, Rebekah Crane, Kinly Posey and Jayden Morton. Posted: Tuesday, October 20, 2015 8:34 am
